{
  "name": "ATLAS — Weekly Market Intelligence Agent",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🌐 ATLAS\n## Weekly Market Intelligence Agent\n\nRuns every **Friday at 7AM UTC**\n\n**What ATLAS does:**\n• Scans industry news & trends from the past week\n• Monitors community discussions (Reddit, HackerNews)\n• Tracks emerging technology movements\n• Reads previous reports to spot patterns\n• Compiles a structured weekly intelligence brief\n• Delivers the brief via email automatically\n\n**Output:** Structured weekly market brief saved to Google Sheets + emailed to team",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "atlas-sticky-overview",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-80, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⏰ TRIGGER\n**Every Friday**\n**7:00 AM UTC**\n\nWeekly cadence ensures\nfresh intelligence without\ninformation overload.",
        "height": 160,
        "width": 200,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "atlas-sticky-trigger",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [320, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🧠 AI BRAIN\n**Claude via OpenRouter**\n\nAnalyses all research\nfindings, identifies patterns,\nformats the brief, and\ndetermines what is\nactionable vs noise.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 220,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "atlas-sticky-agent",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Agent",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [600, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔬 RESEARCH TOOLS\n\n1. **Industry News** — Tavily news scan\n2. **Community Pulse** — Reddit + HN discussions\n3. **Tech Trends** — Emerging tool tracking\n4. **Memory** — Previous reports for pattern detection",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 280,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "atlas-sticky-tools",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Tools",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [900, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📤 OUTPUT\n\n• Save report to\n  Google Sheets\n• Email weekly brief\n  to team inbox\n\nAll reports archived\nfor trend analysis.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 200,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "atlas-sticky-output",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Output",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1280, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 7 * * 5"
